Description:
The Heavy-Duty Gathering Presser Foot is designed for those who require durability and efficiency in their sewing projects. Made from high-quality all-steel material, this presser foot ensures exceptional sturdiness, making it ideal for handling heavy fabrics with ease. Whether you're working with thick upholstery fabric or delicate materials, this foot provides reliable performance, helping to make your sewing projects neater and more professional.

This presser foot is perfect for gathering fabrics, allowing you to sew double-layer gathering with just a single click. The unique design of the foot ensures a perfect gathering effect, giving your projects a polished and precise finish. Its ability to handle different fabric weights makes it a versatile tool, improving your workflow and making gathering tasks quicker and more efficient. Whether you're creating ruffles, pleats, or other gathered designs, this foot will enhance the quality of your work and save you valuable time.

&nbsp;

The 24" Transparent Plastic Ruler is designed for precision and durability. This ruler features a unique sandwich printing technique, where the numbers are printed between two layers of plastic, ensuring they will not rub off over time. The transparent material allows for easy visibility of your project underneath, making it easier to position and mark with accuracy.

Equipped with a zero-centering scale, this ruler is perfect for measurements that require equal space on both sides of a cantered starting point, making it an excellent tool for adjusting pattern sizes or creating symmetrical designs. Ideal for sewing, drafting, or crafting projects, this ruler is an essential addition to your toolbox for professional and precise work.

